THIS IS THE REMOTE PERIPHERAL SERVER (RPS) INFORMATION TEXT FILE.

THIS IS LOOKED UP BY RPS AS     (SYS)RPS.HLP
AND IS USED TO TYPE MOST (90%) OF THE HELP AND DIAGNOSTIC MESSAGES.

FORMAT IS:     <STAR>NAME-OF-TEXT<STAR>
WHICH MUST BEGIN ON A NEW-LINE IN POSITION ONE (1) ALWAYS...

*CAPTXT*

FOR A LIST OF RPS CAPABILITIES, PLEASE CONTACT YOUR LOCAL TYMSHARE
REPRESENTATIVE.

*INSTXT*

FOR A DETAILED LIST OF RPS INSTRUCTIONS, PLEASE CONTACT YOUR LOCAL
TYMSHARE REPRESENTATIVE.

